espot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060179-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120044.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060179\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:56.3%\" href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060179-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120044.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060179\"><img alt=\"The Southern Wilds\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" class=\"js-lazy-load-image\" data-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060179-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120044.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060179-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120044.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060179-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120044.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060179-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120044.jpg 480w\" data-lazy-load=\"false\"><noscript><img alt=\"The Southern Wilds\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060179-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120044.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060179-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120044.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060179-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120044.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060179-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120044.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\"></noscript></a><figcaption>The Southern Wilds</figcaption></figure><h3>Midgard - Well of Urd</h3><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060180-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120111.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060180\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3840px\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" style=\"padding-bottom:56.3%\" href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060180-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120111.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-4060180\"><img alt=\"Well of Urd\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" class=\"js-lazy-load-image\" data-src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060180-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120111.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060180-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120111.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060180-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120111.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060180-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120111.jpg 480w\" data-lazy-load=\"false\"><noscript><img alt=\"Well of Urd\" src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060180-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120111.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/679/6794662/4060180-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120111.jpg 3840w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_super/679/6794662/4060180-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120111.jpg 1280w, https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/679/6794662/4060180-godofwarragnar%C3%B6k_20221108120111.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\"></noscript></a><figcaption>Well of Urd</figcaption></figure><p>With all the Hel Tears closed, your Frozen Sparks will combine into a Frozen Flame, so don't forget to visit a forge as soon as possible to upgrade your Leviathan Axe. Find more <a href=\"/articles/god-of-war-ragnarok-guides/1100-6509005/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6509005\">God of War Ragnarok guides</a> on GameSpot.</p>\n  \n                        \n    \n        <div class=\"js